      "name": "相關訊息",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "人物關係",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "柳橋卓人",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "一位人類武士。千鶴見證了他與妖怪鐮井之間的友誼。當時的千鶴還沒有獲得妖怪的力量。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "鐮井顯治",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "一位妖怪，也是人類武士的摯友。他的力量逐漸讓他與武士在「秋津羽戲」上使用的羽子板中產生了心智。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 7,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Yae Miko_icon.png",
                      "name": "Яэ Мико",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "一位狐妖。曾見過未擁有人形，只是初具神智的千鶴。她使千鶴理解人類與妖怪之間所建立的友誼擁有的意義與價值。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 2263,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Shikanoin Heizou_icon.png",
                      "name": "Shikanoin Heizou",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "懷疑千鶴真實身份的偵探。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3450,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Каппа",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3449,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Ёко",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    },
                    {
                      "amount": 0,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 3448,
                      "icon_url": "",
                      "name": "Хитоцумэ-кодзо",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "千鶴想要保護的小妖怪們。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
